      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Settle the Score!",
        "Client": "Palico Playmate Hunter",
        "Description": "Ever since I got creamed by that\r\nMagma Almudron my Palico doesn\u0027t\r\nwant me hunting. Now that I\u0027ve\r\nrecovered, I wanna take it on\r\nagain and show my Palico that I\u0027m\r\nfine. But now I can\u0027t even get close\r\nto it because of a dang Rajang!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rajang",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Solder les comptes !",
        "Client": "Chasseur au Palico",
        "Description": "Depuis que ce fichu Almudron\r\nMagma m\u0027a battu, mon Palico a\r\ntr\u00E8s peur pour moi. Je me suis\r\nentra\u00EEn\u00E9 depuis, et je voudrais\r\nl\u0027affronter de nouveau,\r\nmais ce fichu Rajang m\u0027emp\u00EAche\r\nde m\u0027en approcher.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Rajang",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Salva i compagni Felyne!",
        "Client": "Cacciatore amico Felyne",
        "Description": "Da quando sono stato sconfitto\r\ndall\u0027Almudron lavico, il mio\r\ncompagno Felyne si preoccupa\r\nmolto. Ora mi sono ripreso e\r\nvoglio ritentare l\u0027impresa, ma\r\nnon posso avvicinarmi per colpa\r\ndi quel maledetto Rajang.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Rajang",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Wieder auf den Beinen",
        "Client": "Palico-Spielkamerad-J\u00E4ger",
        "Description": "Seit ich von diesem Magmadron\r\nzu Brei geschlagen wurde, m\u00F6chte\r\nmein Palico nicht, dass ich jagen\r\ngehe. Ich will ihm beweisen, dass\r\nich wieder der Alte bin, aber ich\r\nkann der Bestie wegen dem\r\nbl\u00F6den Rajang nicht nahe kommen.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Rajang.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00A1Merezco una revancha!",
        "Client": "Cazador amigo de camaradas",
        "Description": "Desde que me derrot\u00F3 ese\r\nAlmudron Magma de marras, mi\r\ncamarada insiste en que no cace.\r\n\u00A1Pero ya estoy curado! Quiero\r\ndemostrarle que estoy bien, \u00A1pero\r\nhay un Rajang de por medio que\r\nme impide ir a por el Almudron!",
        "Target": "Caza un Rajang",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0421\u043F\u0430\u0441\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u041F\u0430\u043B\u0438\u043A\u043E!",
        "Client": "\u041F\u0430\u043B\u0438\u043A\u043E-\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u043D\u0438\u043A",
        "Description": "\u041F\u043E\u0441\u043B\u0435 \u043D\u0435\u0443\u0434\u0430\u0447\u043D\u043E\u0439 \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u044B \u043D\u0430 \u0442\u043E\u0433\u043E\r\n\u043B\u0430\u0432\u043E\u0432\u043E\u0433\u043E \u0410\u043B\u043C\u0443\u0434\u0440\u043E\u043D\u0430, \u043C\u043E\u044F \u041F\u0430\u043B\u0438\u043A\u043E\r\n\u043E\u0447\u0435\u043D\u044C \u043F\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0436\u0438\u0432\u0430\u0435\u0442. \u0422\u0435\u043F\u0435\u0440\u044C,\r\n\u043A\u043E\u0433\u0434\u0430 \u044F \u0441\u0442\u0430\u043B \u0441\u0438\u043B\u044C\u043D\u0435\u0435, \u044F \u0445\u043E\u0447\u0443\r\n\u0432\u043D\u043E\u0432\u044C \u043E\u0442\u043F\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u043D\u0430 \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0443,\r\n\u043D\u043E \u044F \u043D\u0435 \u043C\u043E\u0433\u0443 \u043F\u0440\u0438\u0431\u043B\u0438\u0437\u0438\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u043A\r\n\u0437\u0432\u0435\u0440\u044E \u0438\u0437-\u0437\u0430 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u043A\u043B\u044F\u0442\u043E\u0433\u043E \u0420\u0430\u044F\u043D\u0433\u0430!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0420\u0430\u044F\u043D\u0433\u0430",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
